name: Kush Groove Stationary Cards
description:

</br>*This product is shipped from a third party vendor. Please allow 3 - 5 days for additional shipping.</br>

name: Kush Groove iPad Case
description:
The Kush Groove iPad case for your 2nd, 3rd, or 4th Gen iPad is a one-piece, impact resistant hard shell case featuring an extremely slim profile. The lay-flat feature protects the front of your iPad by extending the bezel above the screen. Compatible with the Apple iPad Smart Cover.

</br>*This product is shipped from a third party vendor. Please allow 3 - 5 days for additional shipping.</br>

name: Kush Groove iPhone Case
description:

</br>*This product is shipped from a third party vendor. Please allow 3 - 5 days for additional shipping.</br>

name: Kushalicious Tote Bag
description:
The Kush Groove Kushalicious canvas tote is made from 100% post-industrial recycled cotton, making it environmentally and socially responsible. The bag measures 13.5" x 15.5" with 5.5" side & bottom gussets and 23" x 1.5" cotton web shoulder straps, which allow you to comfortably carry the bag either over the shoulder or as a tote. All seams and stress points are double stitched for durability, plus there's a pocket inside measuring 5.5" x 6".

</br>*This product is shipped from a third party vendor. Please allow 3 - 5 days for additional shipping.</br>
